LEGAL DESCRIPTION:
22239 Goldcrest Run San Antonio, Texas 78260
NCB 19207 BLK 1 LOT 80 STONE OAK VILLAS SUBD UT-2
Notice is hereby provided that the real property described above (the "Property") is subject to a
continuing lien for the payment of indebtedness owed to The Vistas at Stone Oak Homeowners Association, Inc.
(the "Association"), by the Lot Owner(s) of Record named above for the Current Amount of Unpaid
Indebtedness set forth above, for the nonpayment of certain annual and/or special assessments together with any
other amounts lawfully included in said lien pursuant to the Association's governing documents.
Executed this 30th day of March 2022.

for The Vistas at Stone Oak Homeowners Association, Inc ., known to me to be the person whose name is
subscribed to the foregoing instrument, and acknowledged to me that he executed the same, for the purposes
therein expressed and in the capacity therein stated.
Given under my hand and seal of office on this 30th day of March 2022.
